cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.RO 

This paper is about instance segmentation, which is a computer vision problem. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also proposes a new framework using deep learning methods, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also introduces a new dataset, which could be relevant to cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.RO (Robotics).
